OL,6,FHis statement read: "I was in the
OL,7,Fliving room with my partner and
OL,8,Fchildren. Bella (the cat) was on the
OL,9,Fback of the sofa near my partner. She
OL,10,Fgrabbed it and threw her to the floor
OL,11,Fand it ran into the soft cat tent.
OL,13,F"Bella hissed at me, I don't know why
OL,14,Fbut I threw it up into the air and she
OL,15,Flanded on the floor. I thought it
OL,16,Fwould just get a shock. It had a
OL,17,Fseizure and died in my arms."
